| ShortSummary=A washed-up former Dallas Cowboys player moves into the neighborhood, and no one, not even Hank, can admit that he is a jerk—until the man starts harassing Hank.Guest Stars: Phil Hendrie as Big Willie Lane and Fred Willard as Officer Brown.
| LineColor=FF7F00
}}
