| ShortSummary=A new employee named Rich (voiced by Ben Stiller) becomes popular around Strickland Propane for telling lewd jokes, but Hank feels uncomfortable about them and the lawyer he talks to advises Hank to sue for sexual harassment (since telling raunchy jokes during work hours counts as harassment).  Meanwhile, Dale trades smoking cigarettes for chewing tobacco.Other Guest Stars: Danny Trejo as Enrique
| LineColor=FF7F00
}}
